data.description:
$10,000 in seller credit to be used for closing cost, repairs or even rate buy down!! Back on the market due to no fault of the seller!
Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with a fenced backyard. As you step in you will notice the stunning laminate and tile flooring throughout, creating a modern and easy-to-maintain living space. The home also features two well-appointed bathrooms plus one standout feature of this home is the water filtration system. This property is perfect for those seeking a move-in ready home!
